---
// Second section - quote on the slate/shady-black gradient (no photo).
---
<section id="quote" class="quote">
  <div class="container reveal quote-content">
    <p class="serif quote-main">
      Manche Kämpfe sind unsichtbar.<br />Manche Helden sind klein.
    </p>
    <p class="serif quote-accent">Dieser Song trägt sie.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quote {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    /* shady black fading into the slate grey of the next section */
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 45%, rgba(61, 73, 77, 0.35), transparent 75%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-deep) 0%, #1d2427 55%, var(--bg-night) 100%);
  }

  .quote-main {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .quote-accent {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    color: var(--gold-soft);
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
  }
</style>
